videos.headline: Cincinnati starts off on fire with a 53-yard touchdown
videos.description: Desmond Ridder airs it deep to Tyler Scott for a 53-yard touchdown on Cincinnati's first play from scrimmage.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cincinnati starts off on fire with a 53-yard touchdown) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cincinnati capitalizes on blocked punt with TD
videos.description: Cincinnati capitalizes on a blocked punt with a Jerome Ford rushing touchdown on the drive.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cincinnati capitalizes on blocked punt with TD) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: SMU RB tries to truck defender, ends up fumbling
videos.description: SMU's Tre Siggers tries to run over the defender, but he ends up fumbling and giving the ball back to Cincinnati.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (SMU RB tries to truck defender, ends up fumbling) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ridder keeps it on read-option for 40-yard TD run
videos.description: Desmond Ridder keeps it on the read-option and flies to the end zone for a 40-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ridder keeps it on read-option for 40-yard TD run) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ridder rips pass to Pierce for Cincinnati touchdown
